features.description:
It's used to display a warning icon next to a model name in the model dropdown with a notification message on hover. To add a model and message update the affected_models variant payload. This flag should only be changed by on-call engineers.

Payload format:
{
    "model_notifications": [
            {
                 "model": "MODEL_CHAT_O1_MINI",
                 "message": "Degraded performance"
            }
    ]
}

